-- Barclays to Offer Israel Inflation-Linked Government Bond Index
-- B y   D a v i d   W a i n e r
-- 2010-09-26T12:36:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-26/barclays-to-offer-israel-inflation-linked-government-bond-index.html
Barclays Capital said it will offer
an inflation-linked Israeli goverment benchmark bond index,
according to an e-mailed statement today. The index will allow
investment in an instrument that unifies inflation-linked bonds
in the market, Barclays said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
David Wainer in Tel Aviv at 
 dwainer1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
